# Step 4 - Verify User in Database

Connect PostgreSQL:

```bash
psql -U postgres
```

Select Database:

```sql
\c user_management
```

Check Users:

```sql
select id,
       first_name,
       last_name,
       username,
       email,
       mobile,
       created_at
from users;
```

Expected:

```text
Sudhakar
Sreddyshapathi22
sudhakar@test.com
9876543210
```

User should appear in database.

