# Database Verification Queries

## View All Users

```sql
select * from users;
```

## Count Users

```sql
select count(*) from users;
```

## Search Specific User

```sql
select *
from users
where username='Sreddyshapathi22';
```

## Check Password Stored

```sql
select username,password
from users;
```

Expected:

Password should appear encrypted (BCrypt hash).

Example:

```text
$2a$10$...
```

NOT plain text.

